Emergent Narrative in Magic: The Gathering

I’ve made many memories with Magic over the years - the booster draft I held at the old Wizards of the Coast store for my 8th birthday party, the time I pulled Phage and Akroma in back to back Legions packs, the crazy set I played against a local Radio DJ in a draft at Penny Arcade Expo 2009… but after 15 years with Magic, the memories which stick out the most to me aren’t the epic plays, game-winning top decks, or the the money rares
